9
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:38,860
=Blooms for Her=

10
00:00:38,900 --> 00:00:41,820
=Episode 20=

11
00:00:49,320 --> 00:00:50,119
Jinghe.

12
00:00:54,119 --> 00:00:55,560
Are you all right?

13
00:00:55,799 --> 00:00:56,600
Mei Lin,

14
00:00:57,960 --> 00:00:59,280
let me take you home.

15
00:01:04,879 --> 00:01:06,079
Did he force you to marry him?

16
00:01:06,239 --> 00:01:06,719
No.

17
00:01:06,959 --> 00:01:08,079
I agreed to get

18
00:01:08,640 --> 00:01:11,280
(Population and Land Register)
Zhao's population and land records.

19
00:01:11,620 --> 00:01:13,620
(Population and Land Register)

20
00:01:21,239 --> 00:01:21,920
Your Highness,

21
00:01:22,200 --> 00:01:23,719
Prince Xuanlie is attacking.

22
00:01:23,719 --> 00:01:24,680
Let's take the rear passage.

23
00:01:25,079 --> 00:01:25,680
Come on.

24
00:01:38,040 --> 00:01:38,840
Mei Lin,

25
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:40,640
you lied to me.

26
00:01:54,040 --> 00:01:55,719
(Population and Land Register)
Census records?

27
00:01:56,879 --> 00:01:58,560
Coronation ceremony?

28
00:01:59,239 --> 00:02:00,680
It was all a lie.

29
00:02:01,079 --> 00:02:02,359
You only wanted

30
00:02:02,719 --> 00:02:04,840
to trick me
out of Zhao's surrender letter

31
00:02:06,319 --> 00:02:08,479
to curry favor with Murong Jinghe.

32
00:02:09,199 --> 00:02:10,000
Isn't that right?

33
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:11,080
Yue Qin,

34
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:12,840
even now,

35
00:02:13,159 --> 00:02:14,520
haven't you woken up yet?

36
00:02:16,159 --> 00:02:17,120
You killed Pei Du.

37
00:02:17,439 --> 00:02:18,960
I should avenge him.

38
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:26,080
He was forced.

39
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:28,479
He doesn't deserve to die.

40
00:02:30,719 --> 00:02:32,039
A fallen emperor,

41
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:34,240
living only to endure humiliation
from all.

42
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:36,759
That's the best punishment for you.

43
00:02:41,719 --> 00:02:42,719
I understand now.

44
00:02:45,039 --> 00:02:46,080
Just go.

45
00:02:49,159 --> 00:02:49,960
- Go.
- Go.

46
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:59,919
Your Highness, we found them!

47
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:08,360
Well, well, Jinghe.

48
00:03:08,719 --> 00:03:10,919
You've fallen into my hands after all.

49
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:12,400
Murong Xuanlie,

50
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:15,400
Zhao's surrender letter is in my hands.

51
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:17,199
If you insist on killing me,

52
00:03:17,719 --> 00:03:18,759
how will you

53
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:20,360
explain it to Father?

54
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:22,560
Prince Jinghe died for the empire

55
00:03:22,759 --> 00:03:24,759
and was killed by Zhao traitors.

56
00:03:24,879 --> 00:03:26,639
That's the best explanation.

57
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:31,319
Mei Lin,

58
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:33,560
if you come to me now

59
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:35,400
and beg me to take you away,

60
00:03:35,879 --> 00:03:37,199
I might spare Jinghe's life

61
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:39,479
for a few more years.

62
00:03:49,599 --> 00:03:50,439
Murong Xuanlie,

63
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:53,120
haven't you had enough
of this pathetic show?

64
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:54,599
In this world,

65
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:56,840
there's no worse actor than you.

66
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:58,599
Kill them.

67
00:03:58,879 --> 00:04:00,080
Except for that woman,

68
00:04:00,439 --> 00:04:01,319
kill them all!

69
00:04:27,959 --> 00:04:28,759
Loose!

70
00:04:35,519 --> 00:04:36,319
Leave!

71
00:04:36,879 --> 00:04:37,680
Come on.

72
00:04:46,759 --> 00:04:47,319
No!

73
00:04:47,319 --> 00:04:48,120
Jian!

74
00:04:52,279 --> 00:04:53,079
No!

75
00:04:53,639 --> 00:04:54,439
Jian!

76
00:05:10,900 --> 00:05:12,860
ظآزMoonlight spills like quiet tidesظآز

77
00:05:13,110 --> 00:05:16,080
ظآزA celestial bird
brushes the mountain's edgeظآز

78
00:05:17,940 --> 00:05:19,420
ظآزWings of light drift through the airظآز

79
00:05:19,420 --> 00:05:23,100
ظآزLike blossoms that refuse to fadeظآز

80
00:05:23,880 --> 00:05:26,900
ظآزIt asks no right or wrongظآز

81
00:05:27,140 --> 00:05:29,900
ظآزNor fears the turning of fateظآز

82
00:05:31,020 --> 00:05:32,620
ظآزA trace of spring on the windظآز

83
00:05:32,700 --> 00:05:35,260
ظآزA whisper of a broken heartظآز

84
00:05:37,140 --> 00:05:39,220
ظآزA farewell song unfoldsظآز

85
00:05:39,500 --> 00:05:42,420
ظآزCarrying every sorrow within itظآز

86
00:05:42,820 --> 00:05:44,860
ظآزKarma weaves its endless threadظآز

87
00:05:44,980 --> 00:05:48,820
ظآزAnd I would follow you
without turning backظآز

88
00:05:49,300 --> 00:05:52,300
ظآزLife and death become
nothing sharp or finalظآز

89
00:05:52,620 --> 00:05:55,700
ظآزLove and hate are carried away
on the breezeظآز

90
